For me personally, these\nare important efforts
that I believe create true\ninterdisciplinary conversations
around really wicked problems\nthat we face globally.
And it has really been\nan educative process
to be part of the\ndiscussion in evolving
a format and thrust for a\nsymposium such as this one.
Dr. Enrique Silva from the\nLincoln Land Institute,
who also teaches here at the\nGSD, Alejandro Mazarro, David--
