much bigger than the\ncity, that in fact,
if you go away from the central\ntouristic points in Rio de
Janeiro, most people are living\nin these alternate spaces.
And it really makes\nthat point very clearly.
But that's rare.
In most of these films,\nwhat you're seeing
are these very clear frontiers\nbetween these spaces.
And finally, in all\nof these movies,
